aling contaminated particles.It added that human-to-human transmission is uncommon and has only been documented in limited cases involving specific strains and prolonged close contact.The authority said the advisory forms part of its broader efforts to raise public health awareness among travelers during the busy summer travel season.Weqaya urged travelers to follow official health guidance, review preventive requirements before travel, maintain food and water safety, practice personal hygiene, avoid contact with rodents and contaminated areas, and ensure appropriate health coverage while traveling.The authority also called on the public to rely on official sources for information and avoid spreading rumors or unverified reports, adding that it will announce any public health updates if needed.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["summer travel health saudi", "rodent virus", "saudi public health", "cruise ship virus", "infectious disease monitoring", "weqaya hantavirus", "hantavirus saudi arabia", "saudi health authority"], "creator": ["saudi gazette"], "language": "english", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["top", "crime"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-05-08 18:20:01", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-05-08 18:43:24", "image_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa/saudigazette/uploads/images/2026/05/08/2704729.webp", "video_url": null, "source_id": "saudigazette", "source_name": "Saudi Gazette", "source_priority": 356263, "source_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/saudigazette.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_summary": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "duplicate": false}, {"article_id": "ebe541db48e7a1b031aa7eda9b9c